      "writtenOn": "2014-06-03T05:50:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "actually, i tried several combinations and this one is one of the few that is a little faster.\nThe primary reason for moving these fields first is to keep all the \u0027important\u0027 fields in the same cache-line.\n(now, only eof_ is outside of the cache-line, whereas it was in the middle before, and bits_ was the outlier).\n\n-\u003e added a note",
